title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>As a consequence of the <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00CZ.xml"
addr="jms-00CZ"
title="Fall-through of undefined identifiers">changed fallthrough behavior</fr:link>, several new primitives have been added to the source language, including <fr:code><![CDATA[\p]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\em]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\strong]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\ol]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\ul]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\li]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\blockquote]]></fr:code>, and <fr:code><![CDATA[\pre]]></fr:code>.</fr:p><fr:p>You can add further commands to your primitives using a combination of <fr:code><![CDATA[\def]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\iftex]]></fr:code>, and <fr:code><![CDATA[\xml]]></fr:code>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:tree
